An Act relative to the Athol-Royalston Regional School District Financial Stability Fund.
Be it enacted by the Senate and House of Representatives in General Court assembled, and by the authority
of the same, as follows:
1 SECTION 1. The third sentence of section 2 of chapter 50 of the acts of 2006 is hereby
2 amended by striking out the words “, with the approval of the board,”.
3 SECTION 2. Section 5 of said chapter 50 is hereby repealed.
4 SECTION 3. Notwithstanding any general or special law to the contrary, any and all
5 funds remaining in the Supplemental Reserve Fund to Ensure Fiscal Stability established under
6 section 5 of chapter 50 of the acts of 2006 shall be transferred into the Athol-Royalston Regional
7 School District Financial Stability Fund established under section 2 of said chapter 50 and shall
8 thereafter be subject to all laws, rules and requirements governing said fund.
9 SECTION 4. This act shall take effect upon its passage.
